    {
      "id": "PopularPost182327",
      "post_content": "This could be a board wipe finisher in the same way that Gideon is. It doesn't cost any mana to activate the ability, so play it after a Wrath or DOJ or [Life's Finale](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Life's Finale) when your opponent is down to less than 4 life for the win. Play it on turn 3. Your opponent will either counter something that won't affect them then, or waste enchanment removal on it.",
